# Buildroot hash file for the ados-agent-lite release tarball.
#
# The ados-agent-lite tarball is fetched fresh per build from the
# `lite-agent-main` rolling GitHub Release (rebuilt on every push to main).
# The tarball SHA256 cannot be statically pinned because the release is
# overwritten in place; it changes any time main changes.
#
# Buildroot's BR2_PACKAGE_ADOS_AGENT_LITE_NO_HASH=y must be enabled in the
# defconfig so the package fetch bypasses the hash check on rolling builds.
# When the recipe is moved to a stable tagged release (e.g. lite-v0.1.0), the
# CI workflow at .github/workflows/luckfox-image-build.yml substitutes real
# digests on tag and BR2_PACKAGE_ADOS_AGENT_LITE_NO_HASH=n is restored.
#
# Format (when stable): <algo>  <hex>  <filename>
#
# sha256  <pinned>  ados-agent-lite-lite-agent-main-armv7-unknown-linux-musleabihf.tar.gz
# sha256  <pinned>  LICENSE
